Author: ohmsdeceiver
Text: i pretty much have no muscle left either and it sucks. i feel like my entire body is a blob of fat now. even though i’ve lost some weight, i still look “skinny fat”. i want to try to put on some muscle but i’m so weak and tired all the time so i hardly ever exercise :/
